tlppClass

String tlppClass
The TreebankLangParserParams implementation to use. This is where we get the language pack, and then the GrammaticalStructureFactory used to extract the dependencies from the parse. In most cases you should leave this at the default value, which is suitable for English text.

dependenciesFeature

String dependenciesFeature
The name of the feature to add to tokens. The feature value is a List of DependencyRelation objects giving the dependencies from this token to other tokens.
